    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and represents a solid, dependable choice for someone looking for functional transportation. The engine and transmission are in working order, though you may notice some minor hesitations or noises that are typical for a car of this age and mileage. While the car is reliable for daily use, the exterior shows some wear with visible scratches and minor dings, and the interior has some staining and signs of use. It has been maintained reasonably well, but it will likely require some minor repairs or cosmetic touch-ups in the near future to keep it in peak shape.",
